title: Changing key pair rewards
body:
In line with the forum post https://gov.pangolin.exchange/t/changing-key-pair-reward-multipliers/1705 we are proposing increasing the multiplier to 10x for the following pairs:
* AVAX -ETH.e
* AVAX - USDT.e
* AVAX - DAI.e
author: 0xFd7b8597cF8eE5317439B0B5C55a111F6Eec449D
